fup1.TITLE: Android Homepage UI
fup1.DES: In this project you will get the basic layout of android game homescreen. This can be used for any resolution. Other features are facebook like button,ratting button,credits scane and exit screen. All the sprites used in this project are fresh and clear.

fup2.TITLE: Camera Follow and Zoom
fup2.DES: By this project you can understand basic code to make the camera follow any gameObject. Zoom In and Zoom Out functionalities are also included in this project.
